        "heading": "8 Red flags; 9 Differential diagnosis; 10 Investigations",
        "locator": "pages 12–13; lines 198–235",
        "evidence_summary": "Identifies severe pain or swelling, discoloration, weakness, movement loss, numbness, coldness, deformity, persistent symptoms, fracture or dislocation concern, and clinician-selected radiography, ultrasound, or MRI."
